ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of ELLEN C. DESMOND, Q.C., of Rothesay, New Brunswick, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation for the Atlantic region and Nunavut, effective July 20, 2020.
